cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SE

This paper deals with machine learning attacks on online classifier APIs, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning (cs.AI) and explores the use of active learning (cs.SE) to mitigate the impact of limited training data. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of evasion and causative attacks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and security and privacy (cs.CR) research.
